column2: SELECT TOP # A.ra, A.dec, A.objID, A.z, A.zerr, A.class, A.subClass, A.specobjID, A.specobjIDClean FROM MyDB.CasjobsCombinedOutputCtrl AS A APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (A.RAJ2#, A.DEJ2#, #/#.) AS B LEFT INNER JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS C ON B.objID = C.objID LEFT INNER JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust as D ON C.specObjID = D.specObjID LEFT INNER JOIN galSpecLine as E ON C.specObjID = E.specObjID INTO MyDB.CTRLStellarMassGalSpecLine
